 sucked in by Ingebrigtsen's explosive start - which may ultimately have cost him the gold medal.\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1356, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1217, \"end\": 1226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Online\", \"score\": 0.9923582743238031, \"rank\": 0.007688748966026208, \"text\": \"BBC Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Online\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Online\"}, {\"begin\": 1234, \"end\": 1241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\", \"score\": 0.9533119122966646, \"rank\": 0.048949554718076126, \"text\": \"Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kerr\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1170}, {\"ngram\": \"a new national record time\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1204}, {\"ngram\": \"3:27.79\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1215}, {\"ngram\": \"the Brit\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1255}, {\"ngram\": \"Ingebrigtsen's explosive start\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1303}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold medal\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1355}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I was going crazy up here because we have been talking in the US for quite some time about when our middle-distance runners are going to be able to win major medals,' the legendary US athlete - a former world-record holder in the 200m and 400m - said shortly after the race.\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1633, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1421, \"end\": 1423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.6781947122338935, \"rank\": 0.4716704554792702, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1540, \"end\": 1542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.678194712